 and France's Syssy.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999374022102, \"rank\": 3.144585750961901e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9810630456289974, \"rank\": 0.019270677576128274, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Aussie breaker\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's top B-girls\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not walk away with victories in her round-robin battles.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"victories\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"her round-robin battles\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she did walk away with her creative spirit intact.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her creative spirit\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to ESPN after her performance, Raygun made it clear that she is not here to play by the traditional rules.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.108397093536799e-12, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}, {\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"