owing off their latest tricks.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Social media users\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic breakdancing style\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"an energetic child\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"their latest tricks\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Raygun is not fazed by the jabs, according toDaily Mail.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the jabs\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"toDaily Mail\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All of my moves are original,\\\" she stated confidently.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my moves\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Creativity is really important to me.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Creativity\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I go out there, and I show my artistry.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my artistry\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes it speaks to the judges, and sometimes it does not.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do my thing, and it represents art.\\\"\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my thing\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun's performance sparked a larger conversation about the nature of Olympic breakdancing and the place of creativity in competition.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2004, \"end\": 2010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a larger conversation\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"the nature\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While some were quick to dismiss her Olympic breakdance style as too offbeat for the Olympic stage, others praised her for bringing something new and unique to the floor.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her Olympic breakdance style\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2202}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's chef de mission, Anna Meares, also came to Raygun's defence.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.7932756908862635, \"rank\": 0.26045388560796323, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2342, \"end\": 2353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\